dc_title_s: Railroad map of Michigan prepared for the Commissioner of Railroads by Henry S. Stebbins.
dc_description_s: Prime meridian: Washington. Appears in Michigan Railroad Commission. Tenth annual report. 1882. Inset: [Western Upper Peninsula] 1 map: hand col.; 96 x 73 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
